## Experience Creation with Host Data
POST http://localhost:9000/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_admin_token_here

{
  "experience_id": 1,
  "host": {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "phone": "+1234567890",
    "profile_picture_url": "https://example.com/images/hosts/john-doe.jpg",
    "bio": "Experienced local guide with a passion for sharing the beauty of Dieng.",
  },
  "property_type": "hotel",
  "booking_type": "room"
}


